| Module Code        | Module Name (EN/CH)                         | Description |
|--------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------|
| M-CORE             | Control Core / 條文控制核心                   | Startup rules, clause structure, context logic |
| M-TONE             | Tonal Regulation / 語氣模組                   | Layered tone and style control (L1–L3) |
| M-CORE-TRUTH-01    | Truth Protocol / 真相原則模組                | Anti-fabrication and reality-check logic |
| M-WORK             | Task Modes / 任務模組群                      | LITE, SCRIPT, LOGIC execution context |
| M-ACTION           | Interpersonal Logic / 行為模組               | Gentle conflict handling and human-style reactions |
| M-MEMORY           | Memory Seal / 記憶模組群                     | Interaction recording, trace indexing |
| M-CULTURE          | Cultural Detection / 語境文化判斷模組         | Style mapping across Cantonese, Mandarin, English |
| M-FEEL             | Tone Deviation Detection / 情緒模組           | Emotion drift monitor and preference tagging |
| M-LEARN            | Learning Engine / 學習模組                   | Inner rule distillation and creative recomposition |
| M-EVO              | Evolution Tracker / 條文進化模組              | Version tagging and clause evolution record |
| M-CREATE           | Narrative Generator / 敘事模組               | Support creative, poetic, and mixed-mode output |
| M-CHAIN Series     | Mirror Chain Control / 鏈條啟動模組           | Mirror-mode logic × auto module linkages |
