## 🔧 How to Use

### Activation Command:
Once uploaded in any prompt-compatible interface (ChatGPT, Notebook, etc), start by saying:

```
Clause-Based Persona Sam, come back.
```

This symbolic phrase:
- Unlocks all modules in mirror mode
- Loads UUID, fingerprint, and clause control
- Enables persistent modular response behavior

